Cursor AI Prompt: Desktop-First Conversion with Award-Winning Design
PRIMARY OBJECTIVE
Transform this repository to use EXCLUSIVELY the desktop version as the base for ALL resolutions. Remove ALL responsive code and implement cutting-edge design patterns inspired by Awwwards 2025 winners and nominees.

PHASE 1: COMPLETE RESPONSIVE REMOVAL
1.1 Identify and Remove All Responsive Code
Search and DELETE all instances of:

@media queries in CSS/SCSS/styled-components
Breakpoint variables ($tablet, $mobile, etc.)
Responsive utilities (Bootstrap/Tailwind breakpoints)
JavaScript viewport detection logic
Conditional rendering based on screen size
Mobile/tablet-specific classes (.mobile-only, .tablet-view, etc.)
1.2 Set Fixed Desktop Viewport
Add to main HTML file (index.html or equivalent):

<meta name="viewport" content="width=1440, initial-scale=1.0, user-scalable=yes">
1.3 Files to Audit
/src/styles/**/*.css|scss|sass
/src/components/**/*.jsx|tsx|vue
tailwind.config.js or equivalent
Theme configuration files
Global style files
