2.1 BOLD EXPERIMENTAL TYPOGRAPHY
Implement typography trends from 2025:

/* Oversized Hero Typography */
.hero-title {
  font-size: clamp(4rem, 8vw, 8rem);
  font-weight: 700;
  line-height: 1.1;
  letter-spacing: -0.03em;
  font-variation-settings: 'wght' 700;
