  .dynamic-text {
    font-variation-settings: 'wght' var(--font-weight, 400);
    transition: font-variation-settings 0.3s ease;
  }
}
Typography Requirements:

Use Variable Fonts where possible
Implement kinetic typography (text that responds to scroll/hover)
Add letter-spacing variations for hierarchy
Use mix of weights (100-900) for visual interest
2.2 SOPHISTICATED MICRO-ANIMATIONS
Implement performance-optimized animations inspired by Awwwards Site of the Day winners:

/* Smooth Hover Interactions */
.interactive-card {
  transition: transform 0.6s cubic-bezier(0.34, 1.56, 0.64, 1),
              box-shadow 0.6s cubic-bezier(0.34, 1.56, 0.64, 1);
  will-change: transform;
}

.interactive-card:hover {
  transform: translateY(-12px) scale(1.02);
  box-shadow: 
    0 20px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1),
    0 40px 80px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
}

/* Staggered Animation Entry */
.stagger-item {
  opacity: 0;
  transform: translateY(30px);
  animation: fadeInUp 0.8s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1) forwards;
}

.stagger-item:nth-child(1) { animation-delay: 0.1s; }
.stagger-item:nth-child(2) { animation-delay: 0.2s; }
.stagger-item:nth-child(3) { animation-delay: 0.3s; }

@keyframes fadeInUp {
  to {
    opacity: 1;
    transform: translateY(0);
  }
}
Animation Checklist:

[ ] Intersection Observer for scroll-triggered animations
[ ] Hover states with subtle scale + elevation
[ ] Loading states with skeleton screens (no spinners)
[ ] Page transitions (0.4-0.6s duration)
[ ] Cursor followers on interactive elements
[ ] Smooth scroll behavior (scroll-behavior: smooth)
